title: HoudahSpot 4.0.6 [Cracked] cigoL
description:
Advanced File Search Tool for Mac

Use HoudahSpot to locate hard-to-find files and keep frequently used files within reach.
Start with a simple search. Refine it by adding and combining criteria. Quickly sort through search results. Add columns. Apply filters. Preview files and text matches.
If you've ever had a hard time finding a file before, this is what you've been looking for.

HoudahSpot Features

HoudahSpot builds upon Spotlight, which comes preinstalled with OS X. It makes Spotlight both more powerful and easier to use.
Find files by name, text, content kind, author, recipient, pixel count, etc.
Combine criteria to quickly zero in on the files you are looking for
Search several locations at once. Exclude others
Customize columns in the search results list
Preview files and text matches
Set up templates for recurring searches
